                        <interp inst="t18380917-2125-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 25.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury</hi>.</p>
